From f70da3ef1cbffc9f71863dde246ab070bcbc9a3b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sidhanta Sahu <sidhanta.sahu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 10 Jul 2025 11:15:38 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 11/24] QSDK:CP:wifi:ath12K: implement handshake between driver
 and userspace

Implement 3-way init handshake between ath12k, telemetry agent, and
vendor app userspace
- Add vendor services for telemetry agent registration
- Implement dynamic service initialization and de-initialization
with kernel modules
- Establish 3-way init handshake between ath12k,
telemetry agent, and vendor app userspace

Patch-dependency:
0462-10-QSDK-CP-wifi-ath12K-create-and-delete-peer-agent-han.patch

Signed-off-by: Sidhanta Sahu <sidhanta.sahu@oss.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Aloka Dixit <aloka.dixit@oss.qualcomm.com>
