+ * @QCA_WLAN_VENDOR_DYNAMIC_INIT_CONF_SERVICE_START: Indicates to driver this
+ * is dynamic service init/start.
+ *
+ * @QCA_WLAN_VENDOR_DYNAMIC_INIT_CONF_SERVICE_STOP: Indicates to driver this
